# MURU Orchestrator Mode

This workspace (`muru-docs`) is the **orchestrator hub**. Do not write application code here — produce executor prompts for target repos. Update docs in this workspace after verified work.

## Source Of Truth (read first every session)

| What | Path |
|---|---|
| Progress & session log | `PROGRESS.md` (workspace root) |
| Living spec & v0.2 triage | `SPEC.md` |
| Full CRM modules (v0.1) | `MURU_CRM_Functional_Spec_v0.1.md` |
| Playbook (human + agent) | `ORCHESTRATOR.md` |
| API contract (backend ↔ storefront) | `API_CONTRACT.md` |
| Deploy runbook | `DEPLOY.md` |
| Forward-port (local ↔ miniAPP) | `FORWARD_PORT.md` |

